SharingOverload:
	Board users section:
		- each user can set their avatar and some data

		- each user has their own board, where they post:
			* images
			* text
			* videos ?

		- the post can be reacted and commented

		- each user can send friend request, if someone accepts
			they they will see his/her posts on main page
			and chat

		- there is main page where all your friend's posts go

	Chat section:
		- you can chat with any friend

	Games:
		- challange a friend in game (such as chess)
